  "description": "A group of four pelicans are captured in mid-flight against a soft, overcast sky. The pelicans are silhouetted, displaying their large wingspans and characteristic long beaks. Their wings are spread, showcasing varying degrees of wing curvature as they glide. The background is a uniform pale gray, creating a sense of vastness and openness. The composition emphasizes the birds' dynamic movement and their connection to the air. The lighting is diffused, lending a soft and gentle quality to the scene.",
